snippet.title: Treasure Adventure Game - Final Trailer
snippet.description:
Treasure Adventure Game is a Windows PC Freeware game. 

Created by Stephen Orlando with music by Robert Ellis. 

Download the game now: http://www.robitstudios.com/treasure-adventure-game/

Get the soundtrack: http://robitstudios.bandcamp.com/

Check me out on Twitter: http://twitter.com/#!/robit_studios
